    create a products section which include a sub heading, heading and description text, a row with an adjustable amount of products to show and under this row a button to "See all collections", I need to be able to adjust the border radius of the product card, also to enable or disable a dropshadow effects for the card, the product card should have a content container under the image with the title of the product, price, and "Add to cart" button, I want to be able to change the background color of the card and the border of the card

{% enddoc %}
